Events.Text: Hey I need to reserve a room at the Old Town Inn from May 11th through May 25th.  Can you help me?
You remember that your friend recommended the Hyatt Hotel. Tell the assistant you've changed your mind and want to stay at Hyatt Hotel. [instruction 1 of 5]

Scenario.UserTask: You want to reserve a room at the Old Town Inn from May 11th to 25th. Your name is Alexis. Please do not make a custom request, and it is ok if no room is available - just say goodbye in this case.
Scenario.WizardTask: Help the user reserve a hotel room. (You can find the video tutorial under https://youtu.be/L7QpscLPTFM, in case you want to watch it again.)
